title: Yes To Cucumbers Calming Night Cream, 1.7 Fluid Ounce
description: Yes To Cucumbers calming night cream is perfect for those looking for a dermatologisttested formula to wear overnight that delivers a gentle, hypoallergenic moisture. This lightweight cream combines relaxationinducing ingredients like chamomile and aloe to help relax and calm your senses. Grapeseed oil is an antioxidant rich emollient to help repair and moisturize skin while you sleep. Sweet almond oil provides hydration and cucumbers provide a gentle, calming, silkysmooth finish to skin. You'll wake up with skin that feels soft, pure and calm.
